(D~sub~=1) and [pp1]{acronym-label="pp1" acronym-form="singular+short"}
(D~PP1~=0.5). These conditions decreased the rate of dephosphorylation
roughly by a factor of 5 (41.65 s v/s 200.82 s) (B).

